sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin as Quan tri vien
    participant UI as Admin UI
    participant API as Admin API
    participant Repo as Action Repo
    participant CI as Build/CI
    participant Runtime as Action Runtime
    participant Rasa as Rasa Server
    participant Log as Audit Log

    Admin->>UI: Push hoac chon run actions
    UI->>API: POST /admin/actions/deploy
    API->>Repo: Lay source/version actions
    Repo-->>API: Action code metadata
    API->>CI: Build va test action image/package
    alt Build/test thanh cong
        CI-->>API: Artifact/image tag
        API->>Runtime: Deploy action server
        Runtime-->>API: Healthcheck OK
        API->>Rasa: Cap nhat endpoint actions neu can
        API->>Log: Ghi audit deploy action
        API-->>UI: Actions dang chay
    else Build/test/deploy loi
        CI-->>API: Error
        API->>Log: Ghi audit loi
        API-->>UI: Hien thi loi
    end
